No. 105,

Orig.

Kansas v. Colorado.

Motion of the Special Master for award of interim fees and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $244,063.47 to be paid as follows: 40% by Kansas, 40% by Colorado, and 20% by the United States. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 502 U. S. 1027.3
